[30;1m8155 | [0m[35m        unset the number of new warnings is computed by a more sophisticated[0m
[30;1m8156 | [0m[35m        algorithm: instead of using totals an asymmetric set difference of the[0m
[30;1m8157 | [0m[35m        warnings in the current build and the warnings in the reference build[0m
[30;1m8158 | [0m[35m        is used. This will find all new warnings even if the number of total[0m
